replies.bodyText:
Modified the helper method as following:
		private static boolean lookupJLIPackageCheckDefault(boolean doCheck) {
			/*[IF Java15]
			return false;
			/*[ELSE] Java15*/
			return doCheck;
			/*[ENDIF] Java15*/
		}

This is to skip the package check in JDK15 regardless of incoming doCheck flag while keep same behaviours for pre-JDK15 levels.
Here it invokes lookupJLIPackageCheckDefault(doCheck) instead.

